title: YO Gotti and EST Gee Interview

description:
Today on the show we had Yo Gotti and EST Gee stop by where they spoke about how they first connected, Repping Kentucky, Getting Shot, New Project and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a city council Tommy Bryant for asking “do we have a house n****r in here?” Right before exchange about his wife using n word on Facebook. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during Ask Yee.
